sec.p:
Data derived from the WRS were analysed in order to investigate seven key trends:


the origins of A8 nationals;

the sectoral breakdown of WRS registrations;

the relative importance of A8 migration to particular sectors of the economy;

the geographic breakdown of WRS registrations;

the relative prevalence of A8 migration in regional and local labour markets;

temporal changes in the volume of WRS registrations;

the impact of the recession on immigration from East-Central Europe.
